    "It is important to give the chatbot correct prompts and modify them if the results do not meet expectations.",
    "In addition to the wide range of options in using AI to generate extraordinary ideas, there are threats that can prevent author's creative writing.",
    "The more ChatGPT is used by a human author, the less creative it could be for him personally.",
    "Chatbot offers similar ideas repeatedly, regardless of the genre.",
    "For example, if the story has fantastic components, AI can mindlessly cluster them together, making it difficult to detect strong logical connections (Table 1, Story 4)."
